{
  "stem": "9723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But sometimes, he would also go see them in their houses and then bring the produce with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a doctor, he would, he was allowed to, uh, to go out with a, with a certain permit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had to wear a, uh, a yellow patch-- children, babies in carriages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had to wear a yellow patch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A doctor had, in addition to the patch, a band with a red star of David and, uh, [? arts ?] physician, uh, written on it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I guess had special privileges because of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Uh, I, I remember there was a lot of hunger around, because children would come in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother would cook large pots of soup and other food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And children would come in and, and have a good meal there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, but uh, as time went on, there was more and more starvation, because there is no way to get food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People were given rations but, uh, not very much-- piece of bread for a week or something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lodz Ghetto, I guess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know there was any particular name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember seeing any wall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There must have been some kind of a barricade through which one had to go to, to, to get out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, there was, there was no wall that was built, uh, around there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, there were, uh, Ukrainian police outside, making sure that nobody got out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I said, people could come in, non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then to get out, they had to demonstrate they were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Uh, Jews could come out if they had a, uh, special permit to go out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father could go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Uh, I suppose you could sneak out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did eventually sneak out like, like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
